OL,3,CElusive nightjar's 'remarkable
OL,4,Ccomeback' to South Downs National Park
OL,6,FThe elusive nightjar, nicknamed the
OL,7,F"goatsucker", has made a "remarkable
OL,8,Fcomeback" in the South Downs National
OL,9,FPark following conservation efforts.
OL,11,FThe population of the camouflaged
OL,12,Fbird, known for its "churring" song at
OL,13,Fsunset, is estimated to have doubled
OL,14,Fin the past five years with 78
OL,15,Frecorded last year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]oD@ZOUpD@IO]tD@UOUtD@^O]
