PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773684358
OL,3,CElusive nightjar's 'remarkable
OL,4,Ccomeback' to South Downs National Park
OL,6,FAn ecological survey also found 109
OL,7,Fnightjar territories ` the highest
OL,8,Fnumber recorded ` in the Special
OL,9,FProtection Area in the lowland heaths
OL,10,Fof east Hampshire which includes
OL,11,FWoolmer Forest and the commons of
OL,12,FShortheath, Bramshott, Ludshott,
OL,13,FBroxhead and Kingsley.
OL,15,FA spokesman for the South Downs
OL,16,FNational Park authority said: "They
OL,17,Fare one of Britain's most elusive
OL,18,Fbirds, known for their 'churring' song
OL,19,Fwhen darkness falls and a supernatural
OL,20,Freputation thanks to their mythical
OL,21,Fability to steal milk from goats.
OL,26,@xD@_OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
