PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773684358
OL,3,CElusive nightjar's 'remarkable
OL,4,Ccomeback' to South Downs National Park
OL,6,F"Now the nightjar is making a
OL,7,Fremarkable comeback in the South Downs
OL,8,FNational Park, thanks to nature
OL,9,Frecovery efforts and better habitat
OL,10,Fmanagement."
OL,12,FThe spokesman said that the rise in
OL,13,Fnumbers follows work focused on
OL,14,Fprotecting and increasing lowland
OL,15,Fheath which provides the habitat for
OL,16,Fthe nightjar ground-nesting sites.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773684358
OL,3,CElusive nightjar's 'remarkable
OL,4,Ccomeback' to South Downs National Park
OL,6,FHe added: "Engagement rangers have
OL,7,Falso been out in the landscape over
OL,8,Fthe past decade, encouraging people to
OL,9,Fcare for the landscape, including
OL,10,Fkeeping dogs on leads, picking up dog
OL,11,Fpoo and sticking to pathways to avoid
OL,12,Fdisturbing the nightjars and other
OL,13,Fwildlife.
OL,15,F"The resurgence of nightjars has been
OL,16,Fparalleled by revivals in woodlarks
OL,17,Fand Dartford warblers, which are also
OL,18,Fshowing promising increases in
OL,19,Fnumbers."
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
