PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773684358
OL,3,CElusive nightjar's 'remarkable
OL,4,Ccomeback' to South Downs National Park
OL,6,FEngagement ranger Kirsty Murray said:
OL,7,F"The results of the ecological report
OL,8,Fare so inspiring and really show what
OL,9,Fwe can achieve together to help
OL,10,Fbiodiversity bounce back. It's largely
OL,11,Fdown to the hard work of the land
OL,12,Fmanagers on these sites.
OL,14,F"These lowland heaths were once
OL,15,Fwidespread across the South Downs but
OL,16,Fnow make up just 1% of the national
OL,17,Fpark.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773684358
OL,3,CElusive nightjar's 'remarkable
OL,4,Ccomeback' to South Downs National Park
OL,6,F"They are actually as rare as the
OL,7,Frainforest, supporting some of the
OL,8,FUK's rarest species, so it's really
OL,9,Fimportant we care for the habitats
OL,10,Fthat remain.
OL,12,F"It's wonderful to hear the nightjars
OL,13,Fchurring away as dusk falls and we're
OL,14,Flooking forward to continuing this
OL,15,Fincredibly positive conservation work
OL,16,Falongside local communities and our
OL,17,Fpartners."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
